<br>
Ever tried killing a Cleric without manaburn ?  Heal until I am oom...tough battle *cough.  Yeah, I guess this is fair.<br>
<br>
Oh, what about a Manaburn in a Dungeon ?  This is advantage Wizard ?  Only if I saw you first and hide..<br>
<br>
Trying to land 6 + lures on someone to kill them is so much more difficult than any challeng a melee has in killing me quickly, it is not even comprable.<br>
<br>
If you nerf manaburn, you also have to nerf all the other inherent unbalances that exist in higher level PvP...and there are many, and almost all favor melee's..and then there is the HUGE unbalancing of Melee gear in PvP vs Caster gear in PvP...can you say Fungi Tunic ?<br>
<br>
